reviewText: Grandkids loved it! A few classic Christmas movies with new ones also. Puts everyone in a holiday mood no matter your age.
very intertaining to grandson, he has autism and loves to watch Christmas cartoons even when it isn't Christmas thank you
These were a big hit at my sisters house for the holidays. They remind me of the good times we had when we were children.  Great value for the buck.
There are movies for all ages. I enjoyed watching them along with 5 and 10 year old. Don't have to just watch at Christmas.

great timing and product shipped nicely well done
no damage nice to hand down to grandkids and fair price.  Nice to remember

For $5 I bought this DVD not expecting it to be 'amazing'. To be honest, the DVD is definitly not 'wow' factor but it is a cute dvd. My almost 3 year old loves it even when I was iffy of the quality. There are several shows on there and my daughter loved a few. For $5 I knew I shouldn't expect much.
My son loves this DVD. He wants to watch it every night. Good purchase on my part, good mfg and sell on your part.

We were going to wait to give this to my son for christmas, however we did not. My son likes 4 out 10 of the movies on here. I only  can tolerate the 1st one. The last 6 are put together into a cartoon catergory.

This has been a great DVD for the kids. I will say that I though that I thought they were Christmas shows we had seen before, but they were all old and never before seen.  Several include talking dogs, but overall my 3 and 7 year olds love it.
AAAAAAA
awsome
This was bought to replace the one my Mother-in-law bought for the kids.  The kids love all the movies on it and it nice to see some of the older Christmas cartoons as one of the options to watch.
Great movies for my 2 year old grandson to watch.  It appears he likes all of the movies on the disc and wants to watch them over and over.  Great gift.
This is a nice collection of movies that the whole family can enjoy and watch together without worrying about the content and language for the holiday.
Gave as a gift and the recipient liked it alot so that was a good to hear.  Great deal!  Thanks
I loved the holiday collection, and in good conditions, thank you, I love Christmas, so this worked out well for me
Most of the movies were entertaining for the kids but not all.  Some were very boring. Overall a good value.

These are ok movies for the holidays.  They aren't great but they are an option of some new things to watch w/ the kids at the holidays...Also, they are super cheap so there is your combination...ok movies and super cheap prices, if you like that, your all set!
It will make a perfect Christmas gift for my grandchildren. It sure was a bargain. I will certainly buy again. Very, very pleased with my purchase. Thank you.
